49:11.034 --> 49:15.747
Dear David Bowie,
I wouldn't tell anyone this but you.

49:19.042 --> 49:21.503
Boy, you sure like to read, huh?

49:21.670 --> 49:25.298
My shrink says it allows me
to control something in my life.

49:25.465 --> 49:27.926
This was it,
the moment that would haunt me,

49:28.093 --> 49:32.430
for better or worse,
for the entire rest of my life.

49:32.597 --> 49:36.017
Start with a strand of hair.

49:38.103 --> 49:41.106
She's wearing a hat!

49:44.901 --> 49:48.405
- What are you doing?
- You...

49:53.952 --> 49:57.038
What was next? Caress!

50:01.126 --> 50:05.964
This was not a caress.
This was petting. I'm petting her.

50:11.177 --> 50:14.472
Okay, enough. This was it.

51:03.938 --> 51:07.275
Have you seen Evil Dead II?

51:09.319 --> 51:11.446
No.

51:11.613 --> 51:14.157
It's my favorite movie ever.

51:14.324 --> 51:15.867
You never get to see it in a theatre,

51:16.034 --> 51:18.870
but it's playing at the college
Saturday night.

51:19.037 --> 51:23.583
They don't card anyone there.
Would you want to go?

51:23.833 --> 51:26.753
Sure. I'd love to.

51:27.879 --> 51:30.131
Cool.

51:31.383 --> 51:37.097
All in all, I think it went pretty well.
Your number-one fan, Will Burton.

51:51.986 --> 51:57.283
But it's fun, it's fun.
You know, I've been in a few bands, and...

51:59.911 --> 52:02.330
Boy, you tied the heck
out of that shoe.

52:02.497 --> 52:03.873
Considering it was already tied
and everything.

52:04.040 --> 52:07.293
- Can't be too careful.
- You don't have an inhaler, do you?

52:07.460 --> 52:09.629
'Cause if you do,
you might want to get it ready.

52:09.796 --> 52:11.172
- No!
- Yeah.

52:11.339 --> 52:12.841
You're getting a sneak peek
at the competition,

52:13.008 --> 52:14.426
and I'm not talking Glory Dogs.

52:14.592 --> 52:16.970
Burning Hotels?
But I didn't think there was any way that...

52:17.137 --> 52:20.306
Where there's a will...

52:22.600 --> 52:24.978
Dear David Bowie,
I know it's not saying much,

52:25.145 --> 52:29.899
but this is the coolest thing
that ever happened to me.

52:37.365 --> 52:39.784
I got in, you got out

52:39.951 --> 52:42.537
I walked in, you walked out

52:42.704 --> 52:46.291
As usual I'm stuck in the middle

52:48.335 --> 52:50.920
I'm closer to closure

52:51.087 --> 52:53.715
Admitting that it's over

52:53.882 --> 52:57.469
As usual I'm stuck in the middle

52:59.012 --> 53:01.681
And now you know

53:01.848 --> 53:04.934
That you control everything

53:05.101 --> 53:08.688
As usual I'm stuck in the middle

53:09.773 --> 53:11.941
And now I'm drowning

53:12.108 --> 53:12.984
Where's Will?

53:13.151 --> 53:15.612
In myself again

53:15.779 --> 53:18.198
