54:38.236 --> 54:41.614
I am such a jerk. But it was Burning Hotels!

54:41.781 --> 54:45.577
I had to see the competition.
Don't I get a Burning Hotels pardon?

54:45.744 --> 54:48.038
Tell me one thing.

54:48.204 --> 54:51.624
- Were you with her?
- Yeah.

54:53.960 --> 54:56.046
Are you in love with Charlotte?

54:56.212 --> 54:57.756
What?

54:57.922 --> 54:59.716
- You are.
- I'm not.

54:59.883 --> 55:04.054
- I'm not.
- You had a thing. I don't care.

55:06.389 --> 55:11.519
Look, just remember.
She's trouble. Girls like that always are.

55:11.895 --> 55:15.607
That's ridiculous.
I'm not in love with Charlotte.

55:15.774 --> 55:21.571
You still haven't washed your hand yet.
It was that special, being with her.

55:37.128 --> 55:38.046
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

55:38.213 --> 55:40.298
Sa5m should be home any minute.

55:40.465 --> 55:42.801
What is this project
that you're working on about?

55:42.967 --> 55:48.098
Each other. We're supposed to show
the class who the other person really is.

55:48.264 --> 55:50.517
Yeah.

55:57.565 --> 56:00.860
You sheltered me from harm

56:01.778 --> 56:04.364
Kept me warm

56:05.031 --> 56:07.617
Kept me warm

56:10.203 --> 56:13.289
You gave my life to me

56:14.499 --> 56:17.043
Set me free

56:18.294 --> 56:22.132
It was a competition. She didn't win.

56:23.383 --> 56:26.636
Yeah. Judges were idiots.

56:27.303 --> 56:28.638
Morons.

56:28.805 --> 56:32.225
All the years I had with you

56:32.517 --> 56:36.187
And I would give everything I own

56:39.024 --> 56:42.944
I'd give up my life, my heart, my home

56:45.363 --> 56:48.825
I would give everything I own

56:51.703 --> 56:53.580
What are you doing?

56:53.747 --> 56:56.374
- Here we go.
- What's wrong? That was amazing.

56:56.541 --> 56:59.377
- I can't believe you showed that to him.
- Why not? What's the big deal?

56:59.544 --> 57:01.212
Why are you here?

57:01.379 --> 57:05.342
- I came to apologize again.
- Just go.

57:08.219 --> 57:10.930
She'll forgive you.
I happen to be a girl. I know these things.

57:11.097 --> 57:13.641
Yeah. Okay.

57:16.227 --> 57:20.023
Hey, we got our first post.
"Lower your mortgage rates now. "

57:20.190 --> 57:22.984
Does spam count?

57:32.744 --> 57:35.080
You weren't reading my IM, were you?

57:35.246 --> 57:36.706
You mean the one from Phil
that said "love you"?

57:36.873 --> 57:37.749
- Yeah.
- No.

57:37.916 --> 57:40.168
Good.

57:41.836 --> 57:43.755
He's my dad.

57:43.922 --> 57:48.093
- And you call him Phil?
- That's his name.

57:54.641 --> 57:57.811
Hi. I've been looking for you.

57:57.977 --> 58:00.939
Well, you found me.

58:08.238 --> 58:13.326
I went back up to Hunter Mountain again.
Got stuck on the exact same lift as last year.

58:13.493 --> 58:15.578
No way.
Seriously.

58:15.745 --> 58:19.082
It seems it's not as magical
when you're by yourself.

58:19.249 --> 58:20.709
What'd you do?

58:20.875 --> 58:25.630
Same thing I did last year.
I cried like a little girl.

58:27.007 --> 58:28.633
Listen, Charlotte.

58:28.800 --> 58:31.928
I was thinking that maybe it's time for you
to give me another chance.

58:32.095 --> 58:34.431
Look...

58:36.516 --> 58:41.354
- What's this?
- This is me risking complete humiliation.

58:49.446 --> 58:52.407
Say, won't you stay

58:53.283 --> 58:55.160
We can talk about nothing at all

58:55.326 --> 58:58.163
You are so corny.

58:58.997 --> 59:02.042
Or sit here and make up the words

59:02.208 --> 59:04.919
As we go along

59:06.713 --> 59:09.507
They told me maybe she's crazy

59:09.674 --> 59:12.010
A little like you

59:12.177 --> 59:16.014
Everyone said you were nothing but trouble

59:16.181 --> 59:20.935
And all that I know
is that I've never been here before

59:22.479 --> 59:26.024
I don't need to pretend anymore

59:33.823 --> 59:36.326
Strange, so strange

59:36.493 --> 59:37.660
You are hilarious.

59:37.827 --> 59:41.414
When it feels better being alone

59:41.998 --> 59:45.585
You'll accept there is nobody else

59:45.752 --> 59:48.755
Then set it in stone

