Will and I were just updating our band's
MySpace page.

01:00:16.449 --> 01:00:19.703
You know that kid, Will Burton?
Do some recon.

01:00:19.869 --> 01:00:20.787
Find out everything you can about him.

01:00:20.954 --> 01:00:24.165
They'll have his records in the office.
Where he's from, where he went to school.

01:00:24.332 --> 01:00:27.252
His guidance counsellor report,
that'll have all the good stuff. All right?

01:00:27.419 --> 01:00:28.920
Everything. And do it today.

01:00:29.087 --> 01:00:31.881
Whoa. Yo, dude,
we don't actually work for you.

01:00:32.048 --> 01:00:36.803
It's not like you're the Joker
and we're your henchmen.

01:00:37.512 --> 01:00:40.640
Fine. I'll do it myself.

01:00:40.640 --> 01:00:45.520
All right, best for last. Sa5m, Will?
Tell us who you are.

01:00:54.279 --> 01:00:57.574
My project is Will Burton.

01:00:58.533 --> 01:01:02.996
I'm pointing
because it's hard to tell who he is.

01:01:03.621 --> 01:01:07.125
I was going to use photographs
for this presentation,

01:01:07.292 --> 01:01:12.672
but then I realized, the real Will Burton
can't be captured on film.

01:01:13.965 --> 01:01:16.384
Instead,

01:01:16.926 --> 01:01:19.512
you need this.

01:01:19.679 --> 01:01:23.058
Will is a reflective surface.

01:01:23.224 --> 01:01:27.604
He mirrors back at you
whatever you want to see.

01:01:27.771 --> 01:01:30.815
He reflects you back to you.

01:01:30.982 --> 01:01:34.110
And it's nice for awhile.

01:01:34.277 --> 01:01:36.988
You stop feeling lonely.

01:01:37.155 --> 01:01:41.743
But then you realize,
he's doing that with everyone.

01:01:44.287 --> 01:01:47.999
The only person he can't do it for

01:01:48.333 --> 01:01:49.876
is Will.

01:01:50.043 --> 01:01:53.088
Because he doesn't have a clue

01:01:53.254 --> 01:01:55.757
who he is.

01:02:06.434 --> 01:02:09.312
Okay, well, that was very creative.

01:02:09.479 --> 01:02:13.441
And really mean. Okay, Will, you're up.

01:03:10.081 --> 01:03:13.418
If I told you things I did before

01:03:13.585 --> 01:03:16.838
Told you how I used to be

01:03:17.005 --> 01:03:21.009
Would you go along with someone like me?

01:03:23.762 --> 01:03:27.390
If you knew my story word for word

01:03:27.557 --> 01:03:30.602
Had all of my history

01:03:30.977 --> 01:03:34.981
Would you go along with someone like me?

01:03:36.649 --> 01:03:40.362
And we don't care about the young folks

01:03:40.528 --> 01:03:43.365
Talking about the young style

01:03:43.531 --> 01:03:46.493
And we don't care about the old folks

01:03:46.659 --> 01:03:50.205
Talking about the old style too

01:03:50.497 --> 01:03:54.250
And we don't care about our own faults

01:03:54.417 --> 01:03:57.295
Talking about our own style

01:03:57.462 --> 01:04:00.090
All we care about is talking

01:04:00.256 --> 01:04:03.426
Talking only me and you

